lead_paragraph: Wilton Speight rolled right and threw an interception on his first snap as a starter. When he got his next chance to take the field, Michigan was backed up to its 2.

headline.print_headline: Speight Throws 3 TDs, No. 7 Michigan Routs Hawaii 63-3
